[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "冥途之夢　前篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "人生虛幻縹渺，轉眼即逝。因此人皆為應受庇護之弱者。即使是昔日吾王也非例外。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那應是，與王初次相遇之時。王為了與魔神之戰役而尋求契約龍，因此前來造訪吾之棲所。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吾清楚人類的弱小。在表示讓他珍惜短暫性命後，當時便拒絕了王。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然而，王卻不放棄親自應戰。之後──遭到魔神貫穿了身軀。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──所以，吾才提出忠告的……人類是多麼弱小而可悲的生物。──至少，讓吾為這名男人雪恨吧。正當吾如此決定時……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「還沒完呢……還沒……我必須戰鬥……」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使已遍體鱗傷，他口中所說仍是只注視前方的話語。吾不禁脫口問道。──不畏懼死亡嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「死亡有什麼好怕的。」王笑著回答。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「在你們看來，人的壽命眨眼間就結束了吧。不過……也正因知道生命無常，人類才能夠奮勇向前。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「來不及眨眼的短暫時間……人們必須在那之中由過去繼承希望，並將希望託付給未來才行。若是為了完成這項使命……自己的命，並不足惜！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊啊，看來吾的想法大錯特錯。不捨棄希望，不捨棄鬥志，一心為未來而奮力掙扎之人何來弱小。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這正是人的強大，這正是人生的光輝。如此璀璨的光輝，吾至今從未曾見過。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族之生長似無盡，生命悠久。因此龍族總任時光流逝而飄浮不定。與生之光輝無緣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "此人為了未來正努力掙扎求生。那麼龍族──吾此刻又為何而生？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若與這名男子同行，是否能得出答案？若與這名王者同行，令吾厭倦不已的悠長生命中是否會射入一道光芒？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這道光，這道尊貴的光輝，吾不願就此將其抹滅。既然如此──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──王啊，與吾締結契約吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "藉由與吾締結契約，王保下了性命。吾則選擇未來將與王共同戰鬥至最後。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "接著，命定之日。吾與王共赴了黃泉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 200010011, "title": "冥途之夢　前篇 (200010011)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "冥途之夢　後篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "冥龍‧普魯托。藉由與自身締結契約，拯救了阿爾博流斯的性命。然而，奇蹟卻沒有發生第二次。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使如此，普魯托並不後悔。自己與王共同活過，還找到為王而活這個目標，並得償所願。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "光芒，消失了。此刻剩下的唯有沉入永眠。當他停下行於黑暗道路上的步伐，閉上雙眼時──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「甦醒吧，普魯托。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不可能忘記。也不可能聽錯。是何時出現的呢？眼前竟站著懷念不已的王。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「甦醒吧，普魯托。你還有你該做的事。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──王啊，您在說什麼呢。吾之使命已終結。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吾仍記得。討伐吾等，並繼承吾等意志的年輕王子之姿。既然已有他在，腐朽的吾如今又能做什麼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「你打算殺了我嗎。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "面對吾的迷惘，王開口。「我已將和平的意志寄託給了子孫。但是，如果他倒下了，到時我將會真正地死去。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「為了避免此事發生，活下去，支持他吧。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊啊，吾想起了。這位大人就是如此。不畏懼死亡，眼中總是注視前方，並一心想著如何傳承至未來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因如此，吾才會與阿爾博流斯締結契約。既然如此，他的意志與願望，吾絕不可令其中斷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──遵命。王伸手輕觸吾低垂的頭。雖說已為逝者，卻不可思議地帶著生者般的溫暖。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「你曾救過我一條命。這次就由我接受死亡吧，你甦醒後，離去便是。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吾此刻領悟到，這將會成為最後的交談。──吾王啊，吾將於此道別。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "王放開了手。吾背對王，重新邁開步伐。絕不可回頭。那是違背吾王之言的愚蠢行為。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "感到被光包覆，吾睜開眼。甦醒的雙翼，目標正是懷念的城。「走吧，前往那位王子的身邊。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──所有皆是為了傳承吾王之意志。王啊，請您安祥地沉眠吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 200010012, "title": "冥途之夢　後篇 (200010012)"}]